---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Centricle"
  description="Terms of Service for Centricle products and services."
>
  <div class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10"><em>Last updated: February 28, 2026</em></p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">

        <p class="text-slate-300">
          These terms apply to centricle.com, the portfolio website of Kevin Smith / Centricle LLC. Individual products maintain their own terms of service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">What this site is</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          centricle.com is a personal portfolio showcasing software projects built by Kevin Smith. It includes project descriptions, screenshots, links to live products, and a contact form for professional inquiries.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Contact form</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          The contact form is for professional inquiries — contract work, collaboration, or questions about the portfolio. Do not use the contact form to send spam, solicitations, or abusive content.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Intellectual property</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          The content, design, and code of centricle.com are &copy; 2024-2026 Centricle LLC. Project screenshots depict products that may have their own licenses. The portfolio source code is available under the MIT License on GitHub.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Links to other sites</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          This site links to product sites, GitHub repositories, and third-party services. Each has its own terms and privacy policies. We are not responsible for the content or practices of linked sites.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Availability</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          This site is provided as-is. We make no guarantees about uptime, accuracy, or fitness for any particular purpose. The site may be updated, redesigned, or taken offline at any time.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Centricle LLC is not liable for any damages arising from your use of this site. This is a portfolio — it provides information, not professional advice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Governing law</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Maryland, United States.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Questions about these terms? <a href="/#contact" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">Get in touch</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
